{"title":"Paper. Neutropenia ambulatorio-2025","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/Paper. Neutropenia ambulatorio-2025.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Manejo Ambulatorio de Fiebre y Neutropenia\\Nen Adultos Tratados por Malignidad","guid":"2AuZsOT9dq_t1z4bJ7AHqg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## Propósito","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Proporcionar una guía conjunta ASCO/IDSA actualizada sobre el\\Nmanejo ambulatorio de fiebre y neutropenia en pacientes con cáncer","guid":"vRP28sTQwKrDHLLYserWkw","children":[]}]},{"id":"3","parent":"0","text":"## Población Objetivo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"Pacientes con cáncer que requieren tratamiento de fiebre y neutropenia","guid":"WldxSdMruoDqzFZMXzDcgw","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"## Audiencia\\NObjetivo","guid":"RpWWsB2NQdpmTsBapnzaxw","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"Oncólogos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"Especialistas en enfermedades infecciosas","guid":"NEUQS96DZX_Dt9fIGKEZug","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"Médicos de medicina de emergencia","guid":"4rbVcc88oGibSDZgAs4gBg","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"5","text":"Enfermeras","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"5","text":"Proveedores de práctica avanzada","guid":"dsrBLDiRI367F0euiOCZyg","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"## Definiciones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Neutropenia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Leve: ANC < 1,000/μL (equivalente a < 1.0 × 10⁹/L)","guid":"Yk-GfWtKZfKXod5YRDpxKg","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"Severa: ANC < 500/μL (equivalente a < 0.5 × 10⁹/L)","guid":"pLxbQeaEuJs00cmHpNT4yQ","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"Profunda: ANC < 100/μL (equivalente a < 0.1 × 10⁹/L)","guid":"S3DvJ1ekON-tgns9kEnQNw","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"11","text":"Fiebre en pacientes\\Nneutropénicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Temperatura única oral ≥ 38.3°C (101°F)","guid":"_9Sw5bqqAGg5ZTBCgeQYwQ","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"Temperatura ≥ 38.0°C (100.4°F) sostenida por más de 1 hora","guid":"86gW7whMxAW-BVOmcpb_tw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"0","text":"## Herramientas de\\NEvaluación de Riesgo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"MASCC Score\\N(Multinational Association\\Nfor Supportive Care in\\NCancer)","guid":"8h5HlSitMg_OhgArd3vWDw","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Puntuación ≥ 21 indica bajo riesgo","guid":"FJ5X1KO68IEQkFDYsY9bhA","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"Sensibilidad: 34.8%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"Especificidad: 86.9%","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"19","text":"Reglas de Talcott","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Grupo 4: Pacientes ambulatorios con tumor sólido y bajo riesgo","guid":"CugxGlptdbHckyyzu-WCoA","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"19","text":"CISNE (Clinical Index of Stable\\NFebrile Neutropenia)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Para pacientes que parecen estables con tumores sólidos","guid":"98y0bIamMGptH2I0m_j49A","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Score 0-2: Candidato para manejo ambulatorio","guid":"AgpZjPxZRUrZCkWBdssTWA","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"Score ≥3: Candidato para manejo hospitalario","guid":"u1JV_hgCNhBtVA9-aXE4iQ","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"Sensibilidad: 77.7%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"Especificidad: 78.4%","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"### Pregunta Clínica 1:\\NEnfoque diagnóstico inicial","guid":"RHefwL9Uzgz4x62KC8bX6g","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Asumir infección bacteriana en pacientes con fiebre post-quimioterapia","guid":"3OYrBYEZN2DHk-CsVbxJuw","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Documentar fiebre y obtener muestras de sangre pretratamiento","guid":"Px3dpqMezFBq5kape4wFqQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"Realizar evaluación sistemática en\\Nprimeros 15 minutos del triaje","guid":"","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Historia clínica y examen físico completos","guid":"8-gVxX-ulK6f5sqsbdPdjQ","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"Análisis sanguíneo completo con diferencial","guid":"76I1sEjvGCZ6LmRkk0gJQA","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"Cultivos de sangre (periférico y catéter central)","guid":"qGvSqlA2JNCS1NxAR44USw","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"Estudios de imagen según indicación clínica","guid":"gDZq-ZaeNdGrfn1Z5n5RQw","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"32","text":"Administrar antibióticos empíricos dentro de 1 hora del triaje","guid":"49LzgVnvFjET4hl4RVFmTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"0","text":"### Pregunta Clínica 2:\\NIdentificación de candidatos\\Npara manejo ambulatorio","guid":"XqD8mU1gAylJglv0hUwXqA","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Usar juicio clínico y herramientas validadas (MASCC, Talcott, CISNE)","guid":"609w1bWdlffvywh-cfUNlA","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Criterios clínicos específicos para excluir\\Nmanejo ambulatorio (Tabla 1)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"Cardiovasculares (hipotensión, síncope, etc.)","guid":"yckUOHR-G0w2E_s9k7JSCA","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"Hematológicos (trombocitopenia severa, ANC <100/μL, etc.)","guid":"v4cwP7bMuxkVOsu1lLttvA","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"Gastrointestinales (imposibilidad de tomar medicamentos orales, etc.)","guid":"OHwdMYGqtXipFcR-8V1Mdw","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"43","text":"Hepáticos (función hepática alterada, etc.)","guid":"DXKuwupQXZ2rOQomsuOIQw","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"43","text":"Infecciosos (infección con sitio anatómico claro, sepsis, etc.)","guid":"gla3vGE2R7_WwUsSuYTAnA","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"43","text":"Neurológicos (alteración del estado mental, etc.)","guid":"74s0qZNHNCLrJRtSc6bJWg","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"43","text":"Pulmonares/Torácicos (taquipnea, hipoxemia, etc.)","guid":"nCTscgyy1v5-LKm4i8yp5g","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"43","text":"Renales (función renal alterada, etc.)","guid":"w4HhKzfSR4pKo_xttd1Iag","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"43","text":"Otras comorbilidades significativas","guid":"MSFGR7v3zmsptnRZ1uTCnQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"0","text":"### Pregunta Clínica 3:\\NRequisitos psicosociales y\\Nlogísticos","guid":"f2hDMHUbchCrrgfGOowhsw","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Residencia ≤ 1 hora o ≤ 30 millas (48 km) de atención médica","guid":"5BqOVe-MAUU2xGXUtFVImg","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Médico primario o oncólogo acepta manejo ambulatorio","guid":"2spk5PT7ra_QbvoCGjgmSA","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"53","text":"Capacidad para cumplir\\Nrequisitos logísticos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Visitas frecuentes a clínica","guid":"8CHX9jEa4jWxVLvuPTZGSA","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"Miembro familiar/cuidador en casa 24h/d","guid":"wlHdGRdyB-ezi6Njo9drjg","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"Acceso a teléfono y transporte 24h/d","guid":"TPvUwFxm4zFi0avRnZb9qQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"56","text":"Sin historial de incumplimiento de protocolos","guid":"wsjANnwR4Pgs3r14iltKZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"53","text":"Medidas adicionales\\Nrecomendadas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Evaluación frecuente (≥ 3 días) en clínica/domicilio","guid":"1jSK2NtP6AhVcHME0D-wxw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Contacto telefónico diario para verificar temperatura","guid":"NvbRcKly2MgK0LxTL8Fb1w","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"Monitoreo de ANC y plaquetas para reconstitución mieloide","guid":"wDC8hb3yqlDnQfogxz82lw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"Visitas frecuentes a clínica","guid":"IIE9T8_LMLE5xFErCCCjug","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"### Pregunta Clínica 4:\\NAdministración inicial de\\Nantibióticos y observación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"Primera dosis de terapia empírica administrada en clínica/emergencia/hospital","guid":"XyHADYV6isnVL8OOTvRctg","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"66","text":"Observación por ≥ 4 horas antes del alta","guid":"ZgHapDr1lwmRQ0SGD5Deeg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"66","text":"Pacientes con FN de bajo riesgo pueden\\Nrecibir terapia ambulatoria si:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"La fiebre responde a tratamiento antibiótico empírico IV","guid":"u7JbE-WqeO-73wn6v4cY4w","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"El paciente permanece clínicamente estable","guid":"7CRo6BZW7pONOoK_kJV5fg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"0","text":"### Pregunta Clínica 5:\\NAntimicrobianos recomendados","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Terapia oral con fluoroquinolona (ciprofloxacino o levofloxacino) más amoxicilina/clavulanato","guid":"D2TJ1bws208P08qPnRhu1Q","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Para alérgicos a penicilina: fluoroquinolona + clindamicina","guid":"z7gGlsFi_swtQaUw8xPpWQ","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"No se recomienda monoterapia con fluoroquinolona sola","guid":"90NMJB1pnlB9CkhZzmN4LQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"En áreas con alta prevalencia de bacterias ESBL o resistencia a fluoroquinolonas:","guid":"XQSA1konmAZoQRJCDUmnPg","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"Considerar un carbapenémico para manejo inicial","guid":"7peyjqgnd7VnePmapSaURQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"72","text":"Para infecciones con organismos\\Nresistentes específicos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"MRSA: Considerar adición temprana de vancomicina, linezolid o daptomicina","guid":"MWhDhxkP4aHE3GMiWrLhzA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"VRE: Considerar adición temprana de linezolid o daptomicina","guid":"R6cyxMCb0dxftHuw_QGlLw","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"KPC: Considerar uso temprano de polimixina-colistina o tigeciclina","guid":"8CUWc9vcj4BxGow5djXe_g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"0","text":"### Pregunta Clínica 6:\\NManejo de pacientes que no\\Nmejoran","guid":"vU8HYvvyV-WpLZFIF9iMJg","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Reevaluar pacientes que no mejoran después de 2-3 días de antibióticos","guid":"SIqiscOJWkq2WNdjSgIZCA","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"Considerar\\Nhospitalización si:","guid":"4w2B1GyknzJzRSU3cPyzDw","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Fiebre persistente después de período de defervescencia","guid":"xKD1vR5hG_8Bgz2rRd4H6g","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"Nuevos signos/síntomas de infección","guid":"SuFbkhgOpn624E-Is4Ia4Q","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"No es posible usar medicamentos orales","guid":"IB7U7LuIohxR_Ipr-HaOJQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"Se identifica un patógeno no susceptible al régimen inicial","guid":"OezkXbHvovP2d4OxZm92tg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"0","text":"##\\NConsideraciones\\NAdicionales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Disparidades en Salud","guid":"","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Acceso limitado a atención médica","guid":"BF20hQN2qqGXqU0PNDi8Wg","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"Disparidades raciales y étnicas","guid":"D0zgbBse6cHeZNRNT4HVpA","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"Ubicación geográfica y distancia a centros de tratamiento","guid":"bSaNO1Wndu2wwqQd6iBPgA","children":[]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"89","text":"Condiciones\\NCrónicas Múltiples","guid":"","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","te